### Deployment steps to follow:

1) Build with ng-cli by `npm build --prod`

2) Contents will appear in ./dist folder. Magically !!

3) Take a deep breadth and upload the contents of the ./dist folder on the VPS

   by entering the following cmds:

    $ cd /KALIQ/admin-panel
    $ rsync -r ./dist/ root@45.76.184.39:/home/KALIQ/admin-panel/

4) DAMN !! All is Cool


### Run on the VPS

1) Run the following cmds:

  (Running on port 8080 as daemon )
  $ http-server ./admin-panel -p 8080 &

2) You are a magicial !!

